Step 6:
Open up signlink.java located in the sign folder
search for "public static final String findcachedir()"
and replace the whole code with:
<blockquote>public static final String findcachedir()
{
String s;
String s1;
File file;
s = "C:/ServerName/";
s1 = "";
file = new File((new StringBuilder()).append(s1).append(s).toString());
if(file.exists() || file.mkdir())
{
return (new StringBuilder()).append(s1).append(s).append("/").toString();
}
return null;
}</blockquote>
Replace "ServerName" with the name of your server

Step 7:
In your client search for:
<blockquote>1. "./cache/"
2. "./Files/"
3. "./anim/"
4. "./models/"
5. "./Sprites/"</blockquote>
1. In the java files that have "./cache/" replace "./cache/" with "C:/ServerName/"
2. In the java files that have "./Files/" replace "./Files/" with "C:/ServerName/Files/"
3. In the java files that have "./anim/" replace "./anim/" with "C:/ServerName/anim/"
4. In the java files that have "./models/" replace "./models/" with "C:/ServerName/models/"
5. In the java files that have "./Sprites/" replace "./Sprites/" with "C:/ServerName/Sprites/"

