Step 9:
HTML Code
<blockquote><HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>ServerName</TITLE>
<body bgcolor="black">
<META HTTP-EQUIV="PRAGMA" CONTENT="NO-CACHE">
</HEAD>

<BODY>
<center>
<applet name="ServerName" width="765" height="503" archive="client.jar" code="client.class">
<param name="java_arguments" value="-Xmx1024m">
</applet>

</BODY>
</HTML></blockquote>

Replace "ServerName" with the name of your server and use that HTML on your webhost/VPS/dedi and your done!

